Compare AbstractTensor Types

Source: R/tensor.R
eq_type.Rd

Compare two AbstractTensors for type equality.

Usage

eq_type(e1, e2, ambiguity)

neq_type(e1, e2, ambiguity)

Arguments

e1

(AbstractTensor)
First tensor to compare.

e2

(AbstractTensor)
Second tensor to compare.

ambiguity

(logical(1))
Whether to consider the ambiguous field when comparing. If TRUE, tensors with different ambiguity are not equal. If FALSE, only dtype and shape are compared.

Value

logical(1) - TRUE if the tensors are equal, FALSE otherwise.
